Soros Says in FTD Eurozone Should Form Joint Finance Ministry

-- B y   C h r i s t i a n   V i t s
-- 
2011-09-22T05:44:32Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-22/soros-says-in-ftd-eurozone-should-form-joint-finance-ministry.html
The euro region should establish a
joint  finance ministry ,  George Soros , the billionaire investor,
wrote in  Financial Times Deutschland .  To prepare for a default of  Greece ,  Portugal  and possibly
Ireland, a change of the treaties is needed, including the
implementation of a common entity for raising taxes and issuing
debt, Soros said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Christian Vits in Frankfurt at 
 cvits@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Craig Stirling at   cstirling1@bloomberg.net  